        <mxCell id="U-Ryxw_lpr4LAI1zBOQD-363" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;fontFamily=Zen Kurenaido;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DZen%2BKurenaido;strokeWidth=1;sketch=1;curveFitting=1;jiggle=2;fontStyle=1;textOpacity=60;opacity=50;fontSize=10;" value="ログインと権限付与を自動化し、ユーザーの手間と運用のミスを削減。SSO＋MFAで“安全に簡単”を両立。" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="124" width="70" x="61" y="-1925.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="U-Ryxw_lpr4LAI1zBOQD-364" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;fontFamily=Zen Kurenaido;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DZen%2BKurenaido;strokeWidth=1;sketch=1;curveFitting=1;jiggle=2;fontStyle=1;textOpacity=60;opacity=50;fontSize=10;" value="必要情報に素早く到達。全文検索・絞り込み・権限制御で“速い・正確・安全”を実現。" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="116" width="63" x="137" y="-1925.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="U-Ryxw_lpr4LAI1zBOQD-365" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;fontFamily=Zen Kurenaido;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DZen%2BKurenaido;strokeWidth=1;sketch=1;curveFitting=1;jiggle=2;fontStyle=1;textOpacity=60;opacity=50;fontSize=10;" value="最小権限・暗号化・監査ログで“漏らさない”を標準化。条件付きアクセスや脆弱性対応SLAで事故を未然に防止。" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="117" width="70" x="211" y="-1926.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="U-Ryxw_lpr4LAI1zBOQD-366" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;fontFamily=Zen Kurenaido;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DZen%2BKurenaido;strokeWidth=1;sketch=1;curveFitting=1;jiggle=2;fontStyle=1;textOpacity=60;opacity=50;fontSize=10;" value="マルチAZ/自動フェイルオーバーとDR設計で“止まりにくく、戻れる”を担保。RTO/RPOを数値で保証。" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="104" width="68" x="290" y="-1927.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="U-Ryxw_lpr4LAI1zBOQD-367" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;fontFamily=Zen Kurenaido;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DZen%2BKurenaido;strokeWidth=1;sketch=1;curveFitting=1;jiggle=2;fontStyle=1;textOpacity=60;opacity=50;fontSize=10;" value="オートスケール・停止スケジュール・タグ配賦で“使うときだけ使う”。予実の見える化で急騰を未然に抑制。" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="104" width="68.87" x="447" y="-1928.5" as="geometry" />
